51
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:27,440
And so the solution
to this problem is

52
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:31,290
y of x equals 1 over 1 minus x.

53
00:03:31,290 --> 00:03:33,090
So if you examine
this expression,

54
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:35,340
