61
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:13,670
y equals 1, going to infinity
when approaching x equals 1.

62
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:18,070
But then on the right side
of the value x equals 1,

63
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:21,339
